children.name: SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" T2 ON ("catalogue_product"."parent_id" = T2."id") INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON (T2."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE "offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 126 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_productclass" INNER JOIN "offer_range_classes" ON ("catalogue_productclass"."id" = "offer_range_classes"."productclass_id") WHERE "offer_range_classes"."range_id" = 126 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_category" INNER JOIN "offer_range_included_categories" ON ("catalogue_category"."id" = "offer_range_included_categories"."category_id") WHERE "offer_range_included_categories"."range_id" = 126 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" T2 ON ("catalogue_product"."parent_id" = T2."id") INNER JOIN "offer_range_excluded_products" ON (T2."id" = "offer_range_excluded_products"."product_id") WHERE "offer_range_excluded_products"."range_id" = 126 LIMIT 1

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT DISTINCT "catalogue_product"."id" AS "col1", "catalogue_product"."structure" AS "col2", "catalogue_product"."is_public" AS "col3", "catalogue_product"."upc" AS "col4", "catalogue_product"."parent_id" AS "col5", "catalogue_product"."title" AS "col6", "catalogue_product"."slug" AS "col7", "catalogue_product"."description" AS "col8", "catalogue_product"."meta_title" AS "col9", "catalogue_product"."meta_description" AS "col10", "catalogue_product"."product_class_id" AS "col11", "catalogue_product"."rating" AS "col12", "catalogue_product"."date_created" AS "col13", "catalogue_product"."date_updated" AS "col14", "catalogue_product"."is_discountable" AS "col15" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE ("offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 126 AND NOT (EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 WHERE (U1."range_id" = 126 AND U1."product_id" = ("catalogue_product"."id")) LIMIT 1)))) subquery

SELECT DISTINCT "catalogue_product"."id", "catalogue_product"."structure", "catalogue_product"."is_public", "catalogue_product"."upc", "catalogue_product"."parent_id", "catalogue_product"."title", "catalogue_product"."slug", "catalogue_product"."description", "catalogue_product"."meta_title", "catalogue_product"."meta_description", "catalogue_product"."product_class_id", "catalogue_product"."rating", "catalogue_product"."date_created", "catalogue_product"."date_updated", "catalogue_product"."is_discountable", "offer_rangeproduct"."display_order" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE ("offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 126 AND NOT (EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 WHERE (U1."range_id" = 126 AND U1."product_id" = ("catalogue_product"."id")) LIMIT 1))) ORDER BY "offer_rangeproduct"."display_order" ASC LIMIT 20
